1. Često se igramo u malom parku. (*malom*) (We often play in the small park.)

2. On je svojim malim bratom dao slatkiš. (*malim*) (He gave a candy to his little brother.)

3. Ona je svoju malu kuću uređivala celu nedelju. (*malu*) (She was decorating her small house all week.)

4. Malo dete je zaspalo za stolom. (*malo*) (The little child fell asleep at the table.)

5. Malim dečacima je bilo dozvoljeno da se igraju u dvorištu. (*malim*) (The little boys were allowed to play in the yard.)